# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:13
translate chinese julianap2_bc7d5493:

    # bn "Because she's the only family I have left."
    bn "因为她是我仅剩的亲人。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:14
translate chinese julianap2_c5b70bce:

    # bn "My dad died when I was two. He was in the wrong place at the wrong time and he was shot."
    bn "我两岁时父亲去世了。他当时在错误的时间出现在了错误的地点，结果被枪击身亡。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:15
translate chinese julianap2_f9ad8d11:

    # pc "Wow, I'm so sorry."
    pc "天哪，真抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:16
translate chinese julianap2_2f90a95e:

    # bn "Then my mom died a year later, from a brain aneurysm. She was 25."
    bn "然后一年后，我母亲因脑动脉瘤去世了。她当时才25岁。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:17
translate chinese julianap2_b101b427:

    # pc "That's awful."
    pc "太可怕了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:18
translate chinese julianap2_6266ea9e:

    # bn "Yeah."
    bn "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:19
translate chinese julianap2_8274a334:

    # bn "It was pretty hard. For me and my nana both."
    bn "那段日子真的很艰难。对我来说是，对我奶奶来说也是。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:21
translate chinese julianap2_6e99cf1f:

    # bn "But she's been there for me all my life and I love her more than anything."
    bn "但她一直陪伴着我，我比任何东西都更爱她。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:22
translate chinese julianap2_ec46d221:

    # bn "I couldn't have asked for a better parent."
    bn "我再也找不到比她更好的父母了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:23
translate chinese julianap2_4f3c8e20:

    # bn "She's getting pretty old now though, and her health isn't great."
    bn "不过她现在年纪大了，身体也不太好。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:24
translate chinese julianap2_cb7cc1c6:

    # bn "I worry about her a lot."
    bn "我真的很担心她。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:25
translate chinese julianap2_0e39e951:

    # pc "I understand. That has to be hard."
    pc "我理解。那一定很难受。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:26
translate chinese julianap2_ff56a4eb:

    # bn "It is. But hopefully I still have some time with her."
    bn "确实很难受。但希望我还能陪她一段时间。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:27
translate chinese julianap2_60354ba0:

    # bn "I'm not ready to be all on my own yet."
    bn "我还没准备好完全靠自己。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:28
translate chinese julianap2_1feb4817:

    # pc "I'm here for you. You don't have to be alone. You have a friend in me."
    pc "我在这里陪着你。你不必独自面对。我是你的一位朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:30
translate chinese julianap2_e56b0b77:

    # bn "Thanks, [pcname]. Really. That means a lot."
    bn "谢谢，[pcname]。真的。这对我意义重大。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianap2.rpy:31
translate chinese julianap2_e7fcbcd8:

    # bn "I could use a friend."
    bn "我正需要一个朋友。"

